Global Citizen wrote: “It’s a long and difficult road, so sometimes we fall and fail.
However, like the civil rights and anti-apartheid movements before us, we will succeed because together we are stronger.”
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Sean Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Mona are just some of the star performers who will perform at this year’s festival in New York, with Deborah-Lee Furness and Guy Jackman as the host.
