A unique feature of this personal online data warehouse is that it fully meets the needs of the user who can access any information.
The company calls it “the expansion of personal capabilities through data.”
According to Inrupt CEO John Bruce, the company aims to leverage resources, processes and relevant skills to make the Solid platform accessible to everyone.
